longBusinessSummary: Hilbert Group AB (publ) operates as a fund management company in Sweden. The company is involved in the asset management, proprietary trading, equity investment, and data and analytics, as well as offers managed accounts and white-labelled funds. Hilbert Group AB was incorporated in 2017 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
